20 other relevant biomedical information;
21 (p) "Mine" means any open pit or any underground workings from which coal is
22 produced for sale, exchange, or commercial use, and all shafts, slopes, drifts,
23 or inclines leading thereto, and includes all buildings and equipment, above or
24 below the surface of the ground, used in connection with the workings.
25 Workings that are adjacent to each other and under the same management, but
26 which are administered as distinct units, shall be considered a separate mine;
